# Cursor Rules

This project is governed by the root `AGENTS.md`.

Read `AGENTS.md` at the repository root for:
- Overall philosophy
- Skills, agents, and personas available in `.grok/`
- Coding standards and architecture
- How to work with the monorepo and the two UI apps (staff + public)

Cursor-specific notes:
- The `.grok/` and `agents/` directories contain reusable procedures and definitions.
- For best results, include the root `AGENTS.md` + relevant skill files in your Cursor context when working on agent-related tasks.

See also:
- `CLAUDE.md` for Claude-oriented guidance
- `.github/copilot-instructions.md` for Copilot

Deeper directories may have their own `AGENTS.md` — those take precedence locally.